---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
    title="Tradewise Group | We Run the Business Side. So You Can Run Your Trade."
    description="Tradewise Group is the dedicated business management partner for trade business owners who want to grow, systemise, and exit on their terms."
>

    <!-- =========================================================
         HERO
    ========================================================= -->
    <section class="bg-tradewise-navy text-white min-h-screen flex items-center">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32">
            <div class="max-w-3xl">
                <p class="text-momentum-amber text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
                    For Trade Business Owners
                </p>
                <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight mb-8 text-white">
                    We run the business side. So you can run your trade.
                </h1>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl">
                    Running a trade business is hard enough. Tradewise Group handles the back-end so owners
                    can grow, systemise, and exit on their terms — without drowning in admin, guesswork, or
                    burnout, at a fraction of the cost of in-house overhead.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="https://meetings.hubspot.com/tradewise"
                    class="inline-block bg-momentum-amber text-white font-semibold text-base px-8 py-4 rounded hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-200"
                >
                    Book a Strategy Call
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- =========================================================
         PAIN POINTS
    ========================================================= -->
    <section
        class="relative bg-cover bg-center"
        style="background-image: url('/images/TWG%20website%20image%201.png');"
    >
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-concrete/50"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
            <div class="max-w-2xl mb-14">
                <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-growth-teal mb-4">
                    The Reality for Most Trade Business Owners
                </h2>
                <p class="text-forge-black text-lg">
                    You built something real. But somewhere along the way, the business started running you.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

                <!-- No Time -->
                <div class="bg-white border-t-4 border-momentum-amber rounded p-8 shadow-sm">
                    <img src="/images/TWG%20website%20no%20time%201%20icon.png" alt="" class="w-10 h-10 object-contain mb-4" />
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-forge-black mb-4">No Time</h3>
                    <p class="text-forge-black/70 leading-relaxed">
                        You're on the tools all day, then buried in admin all night. Quoting, invoicing,
                        chasing payments, managing staff drama — there's never enough hours to actually
                        work <em>on</em> the business instead of just <em>in</em> it.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- No Visibility -->
                <div class="bg-white border-t-4 border-momentum-amber rounded p-8 shadow-sm">
                    <img src="/images/TWG%20website%20no%20visability%201%20icon.png" alt="" class="w-10 h-10 object-contain mb-4" />
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-forge-black mb-4">No Visibility</h3>
                    <p class="text-forge-black/70 leading-relaxed">
                        You don't know if you're actually profitable until the accountant tells you —
                        months later. Cash flow is unpredictable, the numbers don't make sense, and
                        you're making big decisions based on gut feel and hope.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- No Plan -->
                <div class="bg-white border-t-4 border-momentum-amber rounded p-8 shadow-sm">
                    <img src="/images/TWG%20website%20no%20plan%20icon.png" alt="" class="w-10 h-10 object-contain mb-4" />
                    <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-forge-black mb-4">No Plan</h3>
                    <p class="text-forge-black/70 leading-relaxed">
                        You know you can't do this forever. But there's no exit strategy, no succession
                        plan, and no clear path to the life you actually want. The business is valuable —
                        you just don't know how to unlock that value.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- =========================================================
         SOLUTION
    ========================================================= -->
    <section class="bg-tradewise-navy text-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
            <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
                <p class="text-momentum-amber text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
                    The Tradewise Solution
                </p>
                <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-growth-teal">
                    One team. Every function. Maximum results.
                </h2>
                <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    Tradewise embeds a dedicated team of business specialists directly into your trade
                    business. We handle all the functions that slow you down, drain your energy, and
                    hold your business back — so you can focus on what you do best, and build a business
                    that runs without you.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-8">
                <p class="text-white/40 text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-8">
                    What We Handle For You
                </p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

                    <div class="border border-white/10 rounded p-6 hover:border-momentum-amber/50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-momentum-amber/10 rounded flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-momentum-amber" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">People & HR</h3>
                        <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Recruitment, onboarding, performance management, payroll, and workplace compliance.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border border-white/10 rounded p-6 hover:border-momentum-amber/50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-momentum-amber/10 rounded flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <span class="text-momentum-amber font-heading font-bold text-lg">$</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Finance</h3>
                        <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Bookkeeping, cash flow management, financial reporting, and profit optimisation.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border border-white/10 rounded p-6 hover:border-momentum-amber/50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-momentum-amber/10 rounded flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <span class="text-momentum-amber font-heading font-bold text-lg">⚙</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Systems</h3>
                        <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            SOPs, job management software, operational workflows, and business process design.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border border-white/10 rounded p-6 hover:border-momentum-amber/50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-momentum-amber/10 rounded flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <span class="text-momentum-amber font-heading font-bold text-lg">↗</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Marketing</h3>
                        <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Lead generation, brand positioning, digital presence, and customer acquisition strategy.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border border-white/10 rounded p-6 hover:border-momentum-amber/50 transition-colors duration-200">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-momentum-amber/10 rounded flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-momentum-amber" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Admin <span class="text-momentum-amber text-xs font-normal">Coming soon</span></h3>
                        <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Answering phones, logging jobs, scheduling, and invoicing — handled for you.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-growth-teal rounded p-6 hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-200">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-white/15 rounded flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Exit Planning</h3>
                        <p class="text-white/80 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            When it's time to step back, we make sure you leave on your terms. We prepare your business to maximise its value, structure the right exit pathway, and ensure you walk away with the return your hard work deserves.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- =========================================================
         HOW IT WORKS
    ========================================================= -->
    <section class="bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">

            <!-- Section header -->
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-6 mb-12">
                <div class="max-w-2xl">
                    <p class="text-momentum-amber text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">The Process</p>
                    <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-growth-teal mb-4">Two paths. One starting point.</h2>
                    <p class="text-forge-black/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">Every engagement starts with a free 30-minute Discovery Call. We listen, we assess, and we prescribe the right path — no obligation, no pressure.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/how-it-works" class="shrink-0 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-growth-teal hover:text-growth-teal/70 transition-colors duration-200 group">
                    See the full process
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 1 & 2 — always the same -->
            <div class="bg-concrete rounded-xl p-6 mb-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-6">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 flex-1">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-tradewise-navy rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-semibold text-forge-black text-sm">Step 1 — Discovery Call <span class="text-forge-black/40 font-normal text-xs">30 min · Free · No obligation</span></p>
                        <p class="text-forge-black/55 text-xs mt-0.5">We understand where you are, where you want to go, and what's in the way.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden sm:block text-forge-black/20 text-lg shrink-0">→</div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 flex-1">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-tradewise-navy rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-semibold text-forge-black text-sm">Step 2 — The Proposal</p>
                        <p class="text-forge-black/55 text-xs mt-0.5">We come back with a clear, tailored roadmap — then your path begins.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden sm:block text-forge-black/20 text-lg shrink-0">→</div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 shrink-0">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-momentum-amber rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-forge-black text-sm">Your path begins</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Two paths -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

                <!-- Business Engine -->
                <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-growth-teal/20 shadow-sm flex flex-col">
                    <div class="bg-growth-teal px-8 py-7 text-white">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
                            </svg>
                            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold">Business Engine</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-white/75 text-sm">We build the back-end so you can build the business.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 flex flex-col flex-1">
                        <p class="font-semibold text-forge-black text-sm mb-1">Which of these sounds like you?</p>
                        <p class="text-forge-black/50 text-xs mb-5">We'll align you to the right starting point.</p>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-6">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 border border-forge-black/10 rounded-lg p-3 hover:border-growth-teal hover:bg-growth-teal/5 transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer group">
                                <img src="/images/TWG%20Website%20Growth%20Ready%20Boss.png" alt="" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover shrink-0"/>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-forge-black group-hover:text-growth-teal transition-colors">Growth-Ready Boss</p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-forge-black/40">Scaling feels messy</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 border border-forge-black/10 rounded-lg p-3 hover:border-growth-teal hover:bg-growth-teal/5 transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer group">
                                <img src="/images/TWG%20website%20Burnt%20out.png" alt="" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover shrink-0"/>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-forge-black group-hover:text-growth-teal transition-colors">Burned-Out Tradie</p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-forge-black/40">Running on empty</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 border border-forge-black/10 rounded-lg p-3 hover:border-growth-teal hover:bg-growth-teal/5 transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer group">
                                <img src="/images/TWG%20website%20Handson%20owner.png" alt="" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover shrink-0"/>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-forge-black group-hover:text-growth-teal transition-colors">Hands-On Owner</p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-forge-black/40">Stuck in the tools</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 border border-forge-black/10 rounded-lg p-3 hover:border-growth-teal hover:bg-growth-teal/5 transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer group">
                                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-growth-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-growth-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                                    </svg>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-forge-black group-hover:text-growth-teal transition-colors">Not sure yet</p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-forge-black/40">Let's find out together</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <a href="https://meetings.hubspot.com/tradewise" class="mt-auto flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full bg-growth-teal text-white font-semibold text-sm px-6 py-3.5 rounded-lg hover:brightness-110 transition-all duration-200 group">
                            Book a Discovery Call
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Exit Planning -->
                <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-tradewise-navy/20 shadow-sm flex flex-col">
                    <div class="bg-tradewise-navy px-8 py-7 text-white">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>
                            </svg>
                            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold">Exit Planning</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-white/75 text-sm">Maximise value and plan your transition out — on your terms.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 flex flex-col flex-1">
                        <p class="font-semibold text-forge-black text-sm mb-1">Quick exit readiness check</p>
                        <p class="text-forge-black/50 text-xs mb-5">Three questions to see where you stand.</p>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-6">
                            <div class="border border-forge-black/10 rounded-lg p-4">
                                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-forge-black mb-3">Are you looking to exit in the next 1–5 years?</p>
                                <div class="flex gap-4">
                                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer text-sm text-forge-black/70 hover:text-forge-black">
                                        <input type="radio" name="q1" class="accent-tradewise-navy"/> Yes
                                    </label>
                                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer text-sm text-forge-black/70 hover:text-forge-black">
                                        <input type="radio" name="q1" class="accent-tradewise-navy"/> Not yet
                                    </label>
                                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer text-sm text-forge-black/70 hover:text-forge-black">
                                        <input type="radio" name="q1" class="accent-tradewise-navy"/> Unsure
                                    </label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="border border-forge-black/10 rounded-lg p-4">
                                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-forge-black mb-3">Do you know what your business is worth today?</p>
                                <div class="flex gap-4">
                                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer text-sm text-forge-black/70 hover:text-forge-black">
                                        <input type="radio" name="q2" class="accent-tradewise-navy"/> Yes
                                    </label>
                                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer text-sm text-forge-black/70 hover:text-forge-black">
                                        <input type="radio" name="q2" class="accent-tradewise-navy"/> No
                                    </label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="border border-forge-black/10 rounded-lg p-4">
                                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-forge-black mb-3">Do you have an exit strategy in place?</p>
                                <div class="flex gap-4">
                                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer text-sm text-forge-black/70 hover:text-forge-black">
                                        <input type="radio" name="q3" class="accent-tradewise-navy"/> Yes
                                    </label>
                                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer text-sm text-forge-black/70 hover:text-forge-black">
                                        <input type="radio" name="q3" class="accent-tradewise-navy"/> No
                                    </label>
                                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer text-sm text-forge-black/70 hover:text-forge-black">
                                        <input type="radio" name="q3" class="accent-tradewise-navy"/> Working on it
                                    </label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <a href="https://meetings.hubspot.com/tradewise" class="mt-auto flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full bg-tradewise-navy text-white font-semibold text-sm px-6 py-3.5 rounded-lg hover:brightness-125 transition-all duration-200 group">
                            Book an Exit Readiness Call
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- =========================================================
         WHO WE HELP
    ========================================================= -->
    <section class="bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
            <div class="max-w-2xl mb-14">
                <p class="text-momentum-amber text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
                    Who We Help
                </p>
                <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-growth-teal">
                    Built for trade business owners at every stage.
                </h2>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">

                <div class="bg-concrete rounded p-8">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full overflow-hidden mb-6">
